snippet.title: Zeta Fighters - Mercury Patch
snippet.description:
Zeta Fighters is real-time multiplayer for mobile devices. Cross-platform touchscreen experience for players who love competitive gaming. Zeta Fighters is available in Germany, Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Finland for both Android and iOS devices. Download Zeta Fighters from: http://www.zetafighters.com/download/

Patch 1504 or Mercury brings many improvements to Zeta Fighters.
Key features include:
- Two new ships (Iku-Turso & Loviatar)
- Two new maps (Harvester & Fusion)
- Daily Missions
- Improved menus
- And much more!

Join the Battle! Check out the leaderboard at http://motu.zetafighters.com/
